Author: nickb
Content: I love S3! It's so easy to get started. I have less use for EC2 since I have less computations to do. I wish I could run a database on EC2...

Author: zaidf
Title: How many teams does YComb invite to Mountain View?

Author: binarybana
Content: I know that YouOS uses it.

Author: pg
Content: We don't accept a fixed number of applicants.  We'll fund anyone who seems good enough.  If we suddenly got 30 great applications, we''d accept them all, and worry later about how to cram them all into our space.

Author: vlad
Content: That's a very great perspective.  I want to be the Ben Folds of my niche.
